### Health check
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Ping
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/ping

###
# SERVICE BOOKINGS
###

### Create a booking
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/service/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_type": "cleaning",
  "description": "My PC is overheating and needs a full dust clean",
  "preferred_date": "2026-03-15",
  "preferred_time": "10:00:00",
  "full_name": "Savvas Savva",
  "email": "savvas@example.com",
  "phone": "99123456"
}

### List all bookings
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/service/bookings

### Get a booking by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/service/bookings/1

###
# BUILDER
###

### Create a manual build
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/builder/builds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "component_ids": [1, 2, 3],
  "include_peripherals": false,
  "notes": "Please double check compatibility before ordering"
}

### List all builds
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/builder/builds

### Get a build by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/builder/builds/1

### Update build status
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/builder/builds/1/status?status=cancelled
